(firstQuint)A Taste and Acceptance Study of FruitiVits in Children Aged 4-8 Years Following a Ketogenic Diet.

.

 The study will involve 12 subjects between 4 and 8 years of age, who routinely use comprehensive micronutrient supplementation as part of their dietary management.

 Primary Hypothesis: FruitiVits is an acceptable source of vitamin, mineral and trace elements for patients on a Ketogenic diet.

 Secondary Hypothesis: FruitiVits will be well accepted and tolerated when given orally to children on a Ketogenic diet.

